## Educational Use Notice

This project is developed for educational purposes as part of the postgraduate 
program at Universidad del Valle. It is intended to demonstrate Firebase 
concepts and mobile development patterns.

Students and educators are encouraged to:
- Use this code for learning and teaching
- Modify and extend the functionality
- Share improvements and fixes
- Create derivative educational materials

Commercial use is permitted under the MIT License terms above.